



<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<title>식품행정통합시스템</title>
<style type="text/css">
body{background-color:#fff;text-align:center;}
body,div,dl,dt,dd,ul,ol,li,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,form,fieldset,p,button{margin:0;padding:0}
body,h1,h2,h3,h4,input,button{font-family:'맑은 고딕',MalgunGothic,Malgun Gothic,Dotum;font-size:18px;color:#333}
img,fieldset,iframe{border:0 none}
li{list-style:none}
img{vertical-align:top}
i,em,address{font-style:normal}
label,button{cursor:pointer}
button{margin:0;padding:0}
a{color:#222;text-decoration:none}
a:hover{color:#0b3e8b;text-decoration:underline;}
button *{position:relative}
button img{left:-3px;*left:auto}
html:first-child select{height:20px;padding-right:6px}
hr{display:none}
legend{*width:0}
table{border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0}
.blind{display:none;overflow:hidden;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:0;height:0;font-size:0;line-height:0}
.off {display:none}
#wrapE {padding-top:150px}
.error{background:url(/common/error_1.png)  no-repeat  -20px 0;padding:90px 0 100px 330px;width:500px;margin:0 auto;text-align:left;	vertical-align:top;	}
.t1 {font-size:30px;margin-bottom:4px;}
.t2 {color:#999}
.tR1{color:#FF1900;}
.logo {margin-bottom:10px;}
.list1 li{margin-bottom:4px;}
.submit {margin-top:10px}
/* btns */
.btn1 {background:#235093;color:white;border:1px solid #0c326a;font-size:18px;padding:0px 5px 6px 5px}
.btn1:hover {background:#356ebf;color:white;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="wrapE">
	<div class="error">
		<h3 class="logo"><img src="logo_h1_01.gif"/></h3>
		<p class="t1">
			지금은 <span class="tR1">시스템 점검중</span>입니다. 
		</p>
		
		<ul class="list1">
			<li>현재 서비스 이용이 <span class="tR1">불가능</span>하니</li>
			<li>양해 바랍니다.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
